headline: CMS Energy Q2 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: CMS beats Q2 earnings and revenue estimates with solid Y/Y growth, backed by higher operating income, and reaffirms its 2025 guidance.

headline: PG&E Q2 Earnings Miss Estimates, Revenues Decline Y/Y
summary: PCG posts Q2 EPS of 31 cents, missing estimates as revenues dip 1.5% year over year to $5.90 billion.
